        <body>
            <pb facs="loc.00050.001.jpg" xml:id="leaf001r" type="recto"/>
            <div1 type="poemNotes">
                <dateline>Decoration Day <lb/>May 30.</dateline>
                <milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>
                <head rend="underline" type="main-authorial">Ashes of Roses</head>
                <milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>
                <milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>
                <l>
                    The <hi rend="underline">dust &amp; debris below</hi>,

                    <lb/>in all the <hi rend="underline">cemeteries</hi>

                    <lb/>not only in Virginia &amp;
                    <lb/>Tennessee but <hi rend="underline">all through

                    <lb/>
                        the land</hi>
                    
                </l>
                <milestone rend="horbar-short-left" unit="undeclared"/>
                <list type="simple">
                    <head type="main-authorial">The names of the flowers.</head>
                    <item>lilacs</item>
                    <item>roses</item>
                    <item>early lilies</item>
                </list>
                <list type="simple">
                    <head type="main-authorial">the colors,</head>
                    <item>purple &amp; white</item>
                    <item>
<del rend="overstrike">&amp; red</del> &amp; yellow</item>
                    <item>&amp; red—</item>
                </list>
                <ab>—the <hi rend="underline">graves</hi>—
</ab>
                <ab>
                    <hi rend="underline">Ashes of Armies</hi>
                </ab>
                <ab>The <hi rend="underline">Unknown</hi>
<add place="supralinear" rend="unmarked">☜</add>
</ab>
                <ab>? <hi rend="underline">Army‑Ashes</hi>
</ab>
                <ab>The dust of each <del rend="overstrike">mingling</del>

                    <lb/>fused <subst>
                            
                                <del rend="overstrike" seq="1">all with</del>
                                                        
                                <add place="supralinear" rend="unmarked" seq="2">in the</add>
                                                    </subst> dust
                    <lb/>of each—(i.e. the rebel &amp; the Union)
                </ab>
                
                <addSpan spanTo="#a1" rend="pasteon"/><q who="#unk" type="printed"><floatingText rend="flat"><body><p><handShift rend="printed"/>Are we to have a National Hy<supplied source="Library of Congress transcription">mn by Cen</supplied>tennial time?</p></body></floatingText></q><anchor xml:id="a1"/>
   
                <pb facs="loc.00050.002.jpg" xml:id="leaf001v" type="verso"/>
                <pb facs="loc.00050.003.jpg" xml:id="leaf002r" type="recto"/>
                <lg type="poem">
                    
                    <head type="main-authorial"><note place="inline" type="authorial">?</note> <hi rend="underline">Ashes of Roses</hi></head>
                    <l>Dust of the dead—</l>
                    <l>ashes of blue &amp; gray,</l>
                    <l>—ashes of battle-pits,</l>
                    <milestone rend="horbar-short-left" unit="undeclared"/>
                    <l>solemn &amp; strange cement—</l>
                    <milestone rend="horbar-short-left" unit="undeclared"/>
                    <l>not a <del rend="overstrike">field</del> crop grows hence in 
                        <lb/>the field, of north or south
                    </l>
                    <l>—<del rend="overstrike">Not</del> Nor moisture of the river,
                            nor
                        <lb/>falling rain
                    </l>
                </lg>
            </div1>
            <pb facs="loc.00050.004.jpg" xml:id="leaf002v" type="verso"/>
